item.title: How to make a .bat file
item.dc:creator: @Marine5287 Marine5287
item.description:
@Marine5287 wrote:

For the first problem, try setting your paths to set your Java. If you don’t already have Java or JDK just go to google and install

those programs. If you already have everything correct with your paths, Java, and JDK then try deleting your paths. For problem

number two, there’s usually two folders. One named client and the other named source.
